             was indicted for <rs id="t17890225-75-off342" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17890225-75-off342" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17890225-75-off342" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17890225-75-cd343" type="crimeDate">2d of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17890225-75-off342 t17890225-75-cd343"></join> one leather hide, value 40 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17890225-75-victim674" type="victimName">
                     Christopher 
                     Croxford
                  <interp inst="t17890225-75-victim674" type="surname" value="Croxford"></interp>
